        "id": 1172779
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-05-04T02:04:02Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Actually, is Crashpad supposed to be \"dropped in\" by replacing all the stuff here:\nhttps://fuchsia.googlesource.com/zircon/+/HEAD/system/core/devmgr/devmgr.c#183\nwith a call to StartHandler()?\n\nIf so, I don\u0027t think there\u0027s any reason we actually have to maintain the same protocol, not that it\u0027s a bad one.",
